{{Flavour|Irresistably prevents a creature from taking any action for a short time, requiring multiple charges but not line of fire.}}

'''Paralysis Gaze''' is a monster-only spell that irresistibly [[paralyse]]s its target, ignoring line of fire. It requires 2 casts to use: the first cast charges the spell, and the second cast paralyses you. The charge cannot be [[dispel]]led, and won't fade away over time, not even if you leave the floor.

The following monsters cast Paralysis Gaze:
*{{monsterlink|floating eye}}

==History==
*In [[0.31]], this spell was replaced with [[Vitrifying Gaze]]. This spell still exists in the game's code, but is currently unused.

[[Category: Monster spells]]
